{
    "418:0": "4 Dharmālokamukhaparivartaścaturthaḥ|",
    "418:1": "iti hi bhikṣavo bodhisattvo janmakulaṃ vyavalokya uccadhvajaṃ nāma tuṣitālaye mahāvimānaṃ catuḥṣaṣṭiyojanānyāyāmavistāreṇa yasmin bodhisattvaḥ saṃniṣadya tuṣitebhyo devebhyo dharmaṃ deśayati sma,",
    "418:2": "taṃ mahāvimānaṃ bodhisattvo'bhirohati sma|",
    "418:3": "abhiruhya ca sarvān tuṣitakāyikān devaputrānāmantrayate sma-saṃnipatantu bhavantaḥ cyutyākāraprayogaṃ nāma dharmānusmṛticaryānuśāsanīṃ paścimaṃ bodhisattvasyāntikāddharmaśravaṇaṃ śroṣyatheti|",
    "418:4": "idaṃ khalvapi vacanaṃ śrutvā sarve tuṣitakāyikā devaputrāḥ sāpsarogaṇāstasmin vimāne saṃnipatanti sma||",
    "418:5": "tatra bodhisattvena caturmahādvīpake lokadhātuvistarapramāṇo maṇḍalamātrādhiṣṭhito'bhūt,",
    "418:6": "tāvaccitrastāvaddarśanīyastāvatsvalaṃkṛtastāvatsuruciro yāvatsarve kāmāvacarā devā rūpāvacarāśca devaputrāḥ sveṣu bhavanavyūheṣu śmaśānasaṃjñāmutpādayāmāsuḥ||",
    "418:7": "tatra bodhisattvaḥ svapuṇyavipākaniṣyandaparimaṇḍite siṃhāsane niṣīdati sma anekamaṇiratnapādapratyupte anekapuṣpasaṃstarasaṃskṛte anekadivyagandhavāsopavāsite anekasāravaragandhanirdhūpite anekavarṇadivyapuṣpagandhasaṃstarasaṃskṛte anekamaṇiratnakṛtaśatasahasraprabhojjvālitatejasi anekamaṇiratnajālasaṃchanne anekakiṃkiṇījālasamīritābhinādite anekaratnaghaṇṭāśatasahasraraṇitanirghoṣe anekaratnajālaśatasahasraparisphuṭe anekaratnagaṇaśatasahasrasaṃchādite anekapaṭṭaśatasahasrābhipralambite anekapaṭṭadāmamālyaśatasahasrasamalaṃkṛte anekāpsaraḥśatasahasranṛtyagītavāditaparigīte anekaguṇaśatasahasravarṇite anekalokapālaśatasahasrānupālite anekaśakraśatasahasranamaskṛte anekabrahmaśatasahasrapraṇate anekabodhisattvakoṭīniyutaśatasahasraparigṛhīte daśadiganekabuddhakoṭīniyutaśatasahasrasamanvāhṛte aparimitakalpakoṭīniyutaśatasahasrapāramitāsaṃbhārapuṇyavipākaniṣyandasamudgate|",
    "418:8": "iti hi bhikṣava evaṃguṇasamanvāgate siṃhāsane niṣadya bodhisattvastāṃ mahatīṃ devaparṣadamāmantrayate sma-vyavalokayata mārṣā bodhisattvasya kāyaṃ śatapuṇyalakṣaṇasamalaṃkṛtam|",
    "418:9": "vyavalokayata pūrvadakṣiṇapaścimottarāsvadha ūrdhvaṃ samantāddaśadikṣu aprameyāsaṃkhyeyāgaṇanāsamatikrāntān bodhisattvān,",
    "418:10": "ye tuṣitavarabhavanasthāḥ sarve caramabhavābhimukhā devagaṇaparivṛtāścyavanākāraṃ devatāsaṃharṣaṇaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ saṃprakāśayanti|",
    "418:11": "adrākṣīt sā sarvā devaparṣad bodhisattvādhisthānena tān bodhisattvān|",
    "418:12": "dṛṣṭvā ca punaryena bodhisattvastena sāñjaliṃ praṇamya pañcamaṇḍalairnamasyanti sma|",
    "418:13": "evaṃ codānamudānayanti sma-sādhu acintyamidaṃ bodhisattvādhisthānaṃ yatra hi nāma vayaṃ vyavalokitamātreṇeyanto bodhisattvān paśyāma iti||",
    "418:14": "atha bodhisattvaḥ punarapi tāṃ mahatīṃ devaparṣadamāmantryaivamāha-tena hi mārṣāḥ śṛṇuta cyutyākāraṃ devatāsaṃharṣaṇaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ yadete bodhisattvā ebhyo devaputrebhyo bhāṣante|",
    "418:15": "aṣṭottaramidaṃ mārṣā dharmālokamukhaṃ śataṃ yadavaśyaṃ bodhisattvena cyavanakālasamaye devaparṣadi saṃprakāśayitavyam|",
    "418:16": "katamattadaṣṭottaraśatam?",
    "418:17": "yaduta śraddhā mārṣā dharmālokamukhamabhedyāśayatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:18": "prasādo dharmālokamukhamāvilacittaprasādanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:19": "prāmodyaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ prasiddhyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:20": "prīti dharmālokamukhaṃ cittaviśuddhyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:21": "kāyasaṃvaro dharmālokamukhaṃ trikāyapariśuddhyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:22": "vāksaṃvaro dharmālokamukhaṃ caturvāgdoṣaparivarjanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:23": "manaḥsaṃvaro dharmālokamukhamabhidhyāvyāpādamithyādṛṣṭiprahāṇāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:24": "buddhānusmṛtidharmālokamukhaṃ buddhadarśanaviśuddhyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:25": "dharmānusmṛti dharmālokamukhaṃ dharmadeśanāviśuddhyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:26": "saṃghānusmṛti dharmālokamukhaṃ nyāyākramaṇatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:27": "tyāgānusmṛti dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvopadhipratiniḥsargāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:28": "śīlānusmṛti dharmālokamukhaṃ praṇidhānaparipūrtyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:29": "devatānusmṛti dharmālokamukhamudāracittatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:30": "maitrī dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvopadhikapuṇyakriyāvastvabhibhāvanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:31": "karuṇā dharmālokamukhavihiṃsāparamatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:32": "muditā dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvāratyapakarṣaṇatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:33": "upekṣā dharmālokamukhaṃ kāmajugupsanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:34": "anityapratyavekṣā dharmālokamukhaṃ kāmarūpyārūpyarāgasamatikramāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:35": "duḥkhapratyavekṣā dharmālokamukhaṃ praṇidhānasamucchedāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:36": "anātmapratyavekṣā dharmālokamukhamātmānabhiniveśanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:37": "śāntapratyavekṣā dharmālokamukhamanunayāsaṃghukṣaṇatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:38": "hrī dharmālokamukhamadhyātmopaśamāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:39": "apatrāpyaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ bahirdhāpraśamāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:40": "satyaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ devamanuṣyāvisaṃvādanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:41": "bhūtaṃ dharmālokamukhamātmāvisaṃvādanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:42": "dharmacaraṇaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ dharmapratiśaraṇatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:43": "triśaraṇagamanaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ tryapāyasamatikramāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:44": "kṛtajñatā dharmālokamukhaṃ kṛtakuśalamūlāvipraṇāśāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:45": "kṛtaveditā dharmālokamukhaṃ parābhimanyatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:46": "ātmajñatā dharmālokamukhamātmānutkarṣaṇatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:47": "sattvajñatā dharmālokamukhaṃ parāpatsamānatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:48": "dharmajñatā dharmālokamukhaṃ dharmānudharmapratipattyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:49": "kālajñatā dharmālokamukhamamoghadarśanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:50": "nihatamānatā dharmālokamukhaṃ jñānatāparipūrtyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:51": "apratihatacittatā dharmālokamukhamātmaparānurakṣaṇatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:52": "anupanāho dharmālokamukhamakaukṛtyāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:53": "adhimukti dharmālokamukhamavicikitsāparamatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:54": "aśubhapratyavekṣā dharmālokamukhaṃ kāmavitarkaprahāṇāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:55": "avyāpādo dharmālokamukhaṃ vyāpādavitarkaprahāṇāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:56": "amoho dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvājñānavidhamanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:57": "dharmārthikatā dharmālokamukhamarthapratiśaraṇatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:58": "dharmakāmatā dharmālokamukhaṃ lokapratilambhāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:59": "śrutaparyeṣṭi dharmālokamukhaṃ yoniśodharmapratyavekṣaṇatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:60": "samyakprayogo dharmālokamukhaṃ samyakpratipattyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:61": "nāmarūpaparijñā dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvasaṅgasamatikramāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:62": "hetudṛṣṭisamuddhāto dharmālokamukhaṃ vidyādhimuktipratilambhāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:63": "anunayapratighaprahāṇaṃ dharmālokamukhamanunnāmāvanāmanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:64": "skandhakauśalyaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ duḥkhaparijñānatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:65": "dhātusamatā dharmālokamukhaṃ samudayaprahāṇāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:66": "āyatanāpakarṣaṇaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ mārgabhāvanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:67": "anutpādakṣānti dharmālokamukhaṃ nirodhasākṣātkriyāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:68": "kāyagatānusmṛti dharmālokamukhaṃ kāyavivekatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:69": "vedanāgatānusmṛti dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvaveditapratipraśrabdhyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:70": "cittagatānusmṛti dharmālokamukhaṃ māyopamacittapratyavekṣaṇatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:71": "dharmagatānusmṛti dharmālokamukhaṃ vitimirajñānatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:72": "catvāri samyakprahāṇāni dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvākuśaladharmaprahāṇāya sarvakuśaladharmaparipūrtyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:73": "catvāra ṛddhipādā dharmālokamukhaṃ kāyacittalaghutvāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:74": "śraddhendriyaṃ dharmālokamukhamaparapraṇeyatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:75": "vīryendriyaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ suvicintitajñānatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:76": "smṛtīndriyaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ sukṛtakarmatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:77": "samādhīndriyaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ cittavimuktyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:78": "prajñendriyaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ pratyavekṣaṇajñānatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:79": "śraddhābalaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ mārabalasamatikramāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:80": "vīryabalaṃ dharmālokamukhamavaivartikatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:81": "smṛtibalaṃ dharmālokamukhamasaṃhāryatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:82": "samādhibalaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvavitarkaprahāṇāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:83": "prajñābalaṃ dharmālokamukhamanavamūḍhyatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:84": "smṛtisaṃbodhyaṅgaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ yathāvaddharmaprajānatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:85": "dharmapravicayasaṃbodhyaṅgaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvadharmaparipūrtyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:86": "vīryasaṃbodhyaṅgaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ suvicitrabuddhitāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:87": "prītisaṃbodhyaṅgaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ samādhyāyikatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:88": "praśrabdhisaṃbodhyaṅgaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ kṛtakaraṇīyatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:89": "samādhisaṃbodhyaṅgaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ samatānubodhāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:90": "upekṣāsaṃbodhyaṅgaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvopapattijugupsanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:91": "samyagdṛṣṭi dharmālokamukhaṃ nyāyākramaṇatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:92": "samyaksaṃkalpo dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvakalpavikalpaparikalpaprahāṇāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:93": "samyagvāg dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvākṣararutaghoṣavākyapathapratiśrutkāsamatānubodhanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:94": "samyakkarmānto dharmālokamukhamakarmāvipākatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:95": "samyagājīvo dharmālokamukhaṃ sarveṣaṇapratipraśrabdhyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:96": "samyagvyāyāmo dharmālokamukhaṃ paratīragamanāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:97": "samyaksmṛti dharmālokamukhamasmṛtyamanasikāratāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:98": "samyaksamādhi dharmālokamukhamakopyacetaḥsamādhipratilambhāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:99": "bodhicittaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ triratnavaṃśānupacchedāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:100": "āśayo dharmālokamukhaṃ hīnayānāspṛhaṇatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:101": "adhyāśayo dharmālokamukhamudārabuddhadharmādyālambanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:102": "prayogo dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvakuśaladharmaparipūrtyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:103": "dānapāramitā dharmālokamukhaṃ lakṣaṇānuvyañjanabuddhakṣatrapariśuddhyai matsarisattvaparipācanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:104": "śīlapāramitā dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvākṣaṇāpāyasamatikramāya duḥśīlasattvaparipācanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:105": "kṣāntipāramitā dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvavyāpādakhiladoṣamānamadadarpaprahāṇāya vyāpannacittasattvaparipācanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:106": "vīryapāramitā dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvakuśalamūladharmāraṅgottāraṇāya kuśīdasattvaparipācanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:107": "dhyānapāramitā dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvajñānābhijñotpādāya vikṣiptacittasattvaparipācanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:108": "prajñāpāramitā dharmālokamukhamavidyāmohatamondhakāropalambhadṛṣṭiprahāṇāya duṣprajñasattvaparipācanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:109": "upāyakauśalaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ yathādhimuktasattveryāpathasaṃdarśanāya sarvabuddhadharmāvidhamanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:110": "catvāri saṃgrahavastūni dharmālokamukhaṃ sattvasaṃgrahāya saṃbodhiprāptasya ca dharmasaṃpratyavekṣaṇatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:111": "sattvaparipāko dharmālokamukhamātmasukhānadhyavasānāyāparikhedatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:112": "saddharmaparigraho dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvasattvasaṃkleśaprahāṇāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:113": "puṇyasaṃbhāro dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvasattvopajīvyatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:114": "jñānasaṃbhāro dharmālokamukhaṃ daśabalapratipūrtyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:115": "śamathasaṃbhāro dharmālokamukhaṃ tathāgatasamādhipratilambhāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:116": "vidarśanāsaṃbhāro dharmālokamukhaṃ prajñācakṣuḥpratilambhāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:117": "pratisaṃvidavatāro dharmālokamukhaṃ dharmacakṣuḥpratilambhāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:118": "pratiśaraṇāvatāro dharmālokamukhaṃ buddhacakṣuḥpariśuddhyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:119": "dhāraṇīpratilambho dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvabuddhabhāṣitādhāraṇatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:120": "pratibhānapratilambho dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvasattvasubhāṣitasaṃtoṣaṇāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:121": "ānulomikadharmakṣānti dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvabuddhadharmānulomanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:122": "anutpattikadharmakṣānti dharmālokamukhaṃ vyākaraṇapratilambhāya saṃvartate|",
    "418:123": "avaivartikabhūmi dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvabuddhadharmapratipūrtyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:124": "bhūmerbhūmisaṃkrāntijñānaṃ dharmālokamukhaṃ sarvajñajñānābhiṣekatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:125": "abhiṣekabhūmi dharmālokamukhamavakramaṇajanmābhiniṣkramaṇaduṣkaracaryābodhimaṇḍopasaṃkramaṇamāra-dhvaṃsanabodhivibodhanadharmacakrapravartanamahāparinirvāṇasaṃdarśanatāyai saṃvartate|",
    "418:126": "idaṃ tanmārṣā aṣṭottaraṃ dharmālokamukhaśataṃ yadavaśyaṃ bodhisattvena cyavanakālasamaye devaparṣadi saṃprakāśayitavyam||",
    "418:127": "asmin khalu punarbhikṣavo dharmālokamukhaparivarte bodhisattvena nirdiśyamāne tasyāṃ devaparṣadi caturaśīterdevaputrasahasrāṇāmanuttarāyāṃ samyaksaṃbodhau cittānyutpadyante|",
    "418:128": "dvātriṃśateśca devaputrasahasrāṇāṃ pūrvaparikarmakṛtānāmanutpattikeṣu dharmeṣu kṣāntipratilambho'bhūt|",
    "418:129": "ṣaṭtriṃśateśca devaputranayutānāṃ virajo vigatamalaṃ dharmeṣu dharmacakṣurviśuddham|",
    "418:130": "sarvāvacca tuṣitavarabhavanaṃ jānumātraṃ divyaiḥ puṣpaiḥ saṃchāditamabhūt||",
    "418:131": "iti hi bhikṣavo bodhisattvastasyā devaparṣado bhūyasyā mātrayā saṃharṣaṇārthaṃ tasyāṃ velāyāmimāṃ gāthāmabhāṣata—",
    "418:132": "tuṣitavarabhavananilayādyadā cyavati nāyakaḥ puruṣasiṃhaḥ|",
    "418:133": "āmantrayate devān pramādamakhilaṃ visarjayata||1||",
    "418:134": "yā kāci rativiyūhā divyā mahasā vicintitā śrīmān|",
    "418:135": "sarvaśubhakarmahetoḥ phalamidaṃ śṛṇurasya karmasya||2||",
    "418:136": "tasmādbhavata kṛtajñā apūrvaśubhasaṃcayaṃ kṣapitveha|",
    "418:137": "mā gacchata punarapāyānasādhvasukhavedanā yatra||3||",
    "418:138": "dharmaśca yaḥ śruto'yaṃ mamāntike gauravamupajanitvā|",
    "418:139": "tatra pratipadyathā prāpsyatha niyataṃ sukhamanantam||4||",
    "418:140": "sarvamanitya kāmā adhruvaṃ na ca śāśvatā api na kalpāḥ|",
    "418:141": "māyāmarīcisadṛśā vidyutphenopamā capalāḥ||5||",
    "418:142": "na ca kāmaguṇaratībhiḥ tṛptirlavaṇodakaṃ yathā pītvā|",
    "418:143": "te tṛpta yeṣa prajñā āryā lokottarā virajā||6||",
    "418:144": "na taraṅgatulyakalpāḥ saṃgīti ca apsarobhi saṃvāsaḥ|",
    "418:145": "anyonyagamayuktā yathaiva sāmāyi kāmaṃ ca||7||",
    "418:146": "na ca saṃskṛte sahāyā na mitra jñātījano ca parivārāḥ|",
    "418:147": "anyatra karma sukṛtādanubandhati pṛṣṭhato yāti||8||",
    "418:148": "tasmātsahitasamagrā anyonyaṃ maitracitta hitacittāḥ|",
    "418:149": "dharmacaraṇaṃ carethāḥ sucaritacaraṇā na tapyante||9||",
    "418:150": "buddhamanusmarethā dharmaṃ saṃghaṃ tathāpramādaṃ ca|",
    "418:151": "śrutaśīladānaniratā kṣāntyā saurabhyasaṃpannāḥ||10||",
    "418:152": "duḥkhamanityamanātmā nirīkṣathā yoniśo imā dharmā|",
    "418:153": "hetupratyayayuktā vartante'svāmikā jaḍābuddhyā ||11||",
    "418:154": "yā kāci ṛddhi mahyaṃ paśyata pratibhāṃ ca jñānaguṇatāṃ ca|",
    "418:155": "sarvaśubhakarmahetoḥ śīlena śrutena cāpramādena||12||",
    "418:156": "anuśiṣyadhvaṃ mahyaṃ śīlena śrutena cāpramādena|",
    "418:157": "dānadamasaṃyamenā sattvārtha hitārtha mitrārthaḥ||13||",
    "418:158": "na ca vākyarutaraveṇā śakyāḥ saṃpādituṃ kuśaladharmān|",
    "418:159": "pratipattimārabhethā yathā ca vadathā tatha karothā||14||",
    "418:160": "mā khalu parāvakāśaṃ svayaṃ yatadhvaṃ sadā prayatnena|",
    "418:161": "na ca kaści kṛtva dadate na cāpyakṛtvā bhavati siddhiḥ||15||",
    "418:162": "samanusmarathā pūrve yadduḥkhaṃ saṃsāre ciramanubhūtam|",
    "418:163": "na ca nirvṛtī virāgo samanugato mithya niyataiva||16||",
    "418:164": "tasmātkṣaṇaṃ labhitvā mitraṃ pratirūpa deśavāsaṃ ca|",
    "418:165": "śreṣṭhaṃ ca dharmaśravaṇaṃ śametha rāgādikān kleśān||17||",
    "418:166": "mānamadadarpavigatāḥ sadārjavāmandavāśca aśaṭhāśca|",
    "418:167": "nirvāṇagatiparāyaṇa yujyata mārgābhisamayāya||18||",
    "418:168": "mohakaluṣāndhakāraṃ prajñāpradīpena vidhamathā sarvam|",
    "418:169": "sānuśayadoṣajālaṃ vidārayata jñānavajreṇa||19||",
    "418:170": "kimapi subahu vadeyaṃ dharmaṃ yuṣmākamarthasaṃyuktam|",
    "418:171": "na ca tatravatiṣṭhethā na tatra dharmasya aparādhaḥ||20||",
    "418:172": "bodhiryathā mi prāptā(syād)",
    "418:173": "dharmaṃ ca pravarṣayedamṛtagāmim|",
    "418:174": "punarapi viśuddhacittā upetha varadharmaśravaṇāya||21|| iti||",
    "418:175": "iti śrīlalitavistare dharmālokamukhaparivarto nāma caturtho'dhyāyaḥ||"
}